</table>
<ul>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/6337781.stm">BBC News Technology</a> Q&amp;A: What is DRM?</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://csclub.uwaterloo.ca/media/Copyright%20vs%20Community%20in%20the%20Age%20of%20Computer%20Networks.html">Copyright vs Community in the Age of Computer Networks</a> by <a href="Richard_Stallman" title="Richard Stallman">Richard Stallman</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.dbskeptic.com/2009/01/18/drm-is-failure-in-action/">Digital Bits Skeptic</a> DRM technology in media publishing</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.microsoft.com/windows/windowsmedia/forpros/drm/faq.aspx">Windows Media DRM FAQ</a> from Microsoft</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.authorama.com/microsoft-research-drm-talk-1.html">Microsoft Research DRM talk</a>, by Cory Doctorow</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.reckon.co.uk/open/iTunes">iTunes, DRM and competition law</a> by Reckon LLP</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://europa.eu/comm/enterprise/ict/policy/doc/drm.pdf">Digital Rights Management</a> from CEN/ISSS (European Committee for Standardization / Information Society Standardization System). Contains a range of possible definitions for DRM from various stakeholders. 30 September 2003</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.tweakguides.com/Piracy_1.html">PC Game Piracy Examined</a> Article investigating the effects of DRM and piracy on the video game industry</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://drm.info">DRM.info</a> Information about DRM by <a href="Chaos_Computer_Club" title="Chaos Computer Club">Chaos Computer Club</a>, <a href="Defective_by_design" title="Defective by design" class="mw-redirect">Defective by design</a>, <a href="Electronic_Frontier_Foundation" title="Electronic Frontier Foundation">Electronic Frontier Foundation</a>, <a href="Free_Software_Foundation_Europe" title="Free Software Foundation Europe">Free Software Foundation Europe</a>, and other organisations.</li>
</ul>
